---
// Import required dependencies
import Image from "astro:assets";
---

<section id="about" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-no-repeat bg-left-bottom bg-fixed">
  <div
    class="container mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col items-center space-y-8 md:flex-row md:space-y-0 md:space-x-8"
  >
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left">
      <h2
        class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-sm uppercase font-bold mb-2"
        data-aos="slide-up"
        data-aos-offset="120"
        data-aos-duration="400"
        data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
        data-aos-once="true"
      >
        Wilderness Connections
      </h2>
      <h3
        class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
        data-aos="slide-up"
        data-aos-delay="50"
        data-aos-duration="400"
        data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
        data-aos-once="true"
      >
        Dicover our Mission
      </h3>
      <p
        class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6"
        data-aos="slide-up"
        data-aos-delay="100"
        data-aos-duration="400"
        data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
        data-aos-once="true"
      >
        At Wilderness Connections, our mission is to inspire teens to step away
        from their screens and reconnect with the natural world. Through
        immersive outdoor adventures, we provide opportunities to explore
        breathtaking landscapes, build lasting friendships, and develop a deep
        appreciation for nature. Guided by experienced mentors, participants
        gain valuable life skills, self-confidence, and a sense of belonging
        while discovering the beauty and interconnectedness of the world around
        them. Join us in fostering a generation that cherishes and protects the
        planet by making real-world connections in the great outdoors
      </p>
      <a
        href={`https://wa.me/13525028826`}
        class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 underline font-semibold"
        data-aos="slide-up"
        data-aos-delay="200"
        data-aos-duration="400"
        data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
        data-aos-once="true"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
    <div
      class="w-full md:w-1/2"
      data-aos="fade-in"
      data-aos-offset="120"
      data-aos-duration="400"
      data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
      data-aos-once="true"
    >
      <img
        src="/img/aboutwc.webp"
        alt="About Section Image"
        class="rounded-lg shadow-lg"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
